@startuml
title MicroMeet - Activity Diagram (Authenticate User - Login)

start
:1. Open Login screen;
:2. Enter username and password;
:3. Click "Login";
:4. System validates input format;

if (Input valid?) then (Yes)
  :5. System finds user by username;
  if (User exists?) then (Yes)
    :6. System verifies password;
    if (Password correct?) then (Yes)
      :7. Create session/token;
      :8. Show Home screen;
    else (No)
      :9. Show "Invalid credentials" error;
    endif
  else (No)
    :10. Show "Invalid credentials" error;
  endif
else (No)
  :11. Show validation errors;
endif

stop

legend bottom
Steps mapping (numbers match actions):
1 Open login screen
2 Enter credentials
3 Submit login
4 Validate input format
5 Find user
6 Verify password
7 Create session/token
8 Show home screen
9 Invalid credentials error
10 User not found error
11 Validation errors
endlegend

@enduml